---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Avant Beetle CTRL ALT RESIST" description="Avant Beetle CTRL ALT RESIST" />
		<style>

			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				display: flex;
				font-size: 14px;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				min-height: 100vh;

			}
			.content {
				flex-grow: 1;
				padding: 60px;
				max-width: 800px;
				width: 100%;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			.game-section {
				margin-bottom: 60px;
			}
			.game-title {
				font-size: 24px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;


			}
			
			.image-gallery {
				display: flex;
				overflow-x: auto;
				gap: 20px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
				-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
			}
			.gallery-item {
				flex: 0 0 auto;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 533px;
				height: 300px;
			}
			.gallery-video {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
			}
			.gallery-image {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				object-fit: cover;
			}
			.game-description {
				max-width: 600px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;
				white-space: pre-wrap;

			}
			.game-credits {
				margin-top: 12px;
				max-width: 600px;
			}
			.game-credits ul {
				margin: 4px 0 0 0;
				padding-left: 20px;
			}
			.video-embed {
				position: relative;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 600px;
				padding-top: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
				margin: 20px 0;
			}
			.video-embed iframe {
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				border: 0;
			}
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				body {
					flex-direction: column;
				}
				.content {
					padding: 20px;
				}
				.game-title {
					font-size: 20px;
				}
				.gallery-item {
					height: 56.25vw; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
					max-height: 300px;
				}
				.game-description {
					font-size: 14px;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Sidebar />
		<div class="content">
			<strong>RESIST RESIST RESIST at Avant Beetle CTRL ALT RESIST Exhibition</strong>
            <br>
            Atlanta, US
            <br>
            2025
			<p>
CTRL ALT RESIST was a three-day videogame exhibition highlighting games as a tool for protest, political resistance, and radical imagination; elevating play as a political act, presented by <a href="https://avantbeetle.com/">Avant Beetle.</a>
</p>
<p>
Presented during a time of political unease and collective uncertainty, CTRL ALT RESIST positions games as frameworks for dialogue and dissent. Here, play becomes a means of reflection, confrontation, and possibility.
</p>
<p>
The games featured come from developers across the globe, each offering a distinct voice and vision. From deeply personal experiences to collective struggles.Together, they demonstrate the powerful potential of games to move, provoke, and inspire action.
</p>

            <img  src="/ctrl-alt-resist/poster.webp"/>

			<img  src="/ctrl-alt-resist/website.webp"/>

			<!-- <div style="width: 25%;">
			<img src="/Written-By-a-Human-Not-By-AI-Badge-white@2x.png" alt="Your Image">
			</div> -->

		</div>
	</body>
</html>